name: Organised File Template for Team
description:
This organised file’s objective is to give designers their own personal space for designing the screens and the leads or PM’s can easily see the progress of what is being done, by who, where to find them at a single place.


This will also help developers to find the pages in a single glance. If they have any questions, they exactly know which designer to contact.


Open for any suggestions.


Contact: chaithzx@icloud.com
